Class Inventory

    • addPart

      public static void addPart(Part newPart)
      Adds a Part to the allParts list. LOGIC ERROR Unable to generate a unique Part ID. Corrected by sorting allParts by Part ID's with a bubble sort and finding the highest Part ID then assigning a new Part an ID that is 1 more than the highest ID.
      Parameters:
      newPart - The new Part to add to allParts.
